summary: This document is a calendar entry for a scheduled call between the FBI and the Southern District of New York (SDNY) regarding discovery in the Epstein investigation. It indicates ongoing coordination between federal agencies on the case in late 2020.

events.title: Call between FBI and SDNY on Epstein discovery
events.description: A scheduled call to discuss discovery matters related to the Epstein investigation.

keyFacts: The FBI and SDNY were coordinating on discovery in the Epstein investigation as of October 2020.
The call was scheduled for October 23, 2020, from 3:00 PM to 3:30 PM.
The document is a calendar entry, indicating planned inter-agency communication.
